Program: The Why Factor
Title: Touch
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01qh9dr
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 3 Feb 2014
Why do we touch each other? And how do different cultures view physical contact in everyday life? Mike Williams explores our least-studied sense and meets a woman who gets her fill of human contact by cuddling people she has just met. (Image: A mother and daughter hold hands. Credit: Getty Images) Show less